  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1101800/extras/2551fa7c0d130fd64aa83c938686fd98.webp?t=1602840909\" width=180 height=50 /></span><br><br>10mg is a collection of 10 minute long games.<br>Always Down is about going away.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1101800/extras/d7c9289a79a4ed11ade94a59b9387769.webp?t=1602840909\" width=396 height=56 /></span><br><br>You solve easy puzzles and overcome light platforming challenges as you go Always Down.<br>The deeper you dissapear into the cave, the more you change.<br>You can do things you could have never thought to be possible!<br><br>... but<br><br><strong>is it really worth it?</strong><br><br>Always down is a ~10 minute long meditation on change that will stay with you for a long time.<br><br>The Steam Capsule Image was created by the wonderful @_cobywin",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1101800/extras/2551fa7c0d130fd64aa83c938686fd98.webp?t=1602840909\" width=180 height=50 /></span><br><br>10mg is a collection of 10 minute long games.<br>Always Down is about going away.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1101800/extras/d7c9289a79a4ed11ade94a59b9387769.webp?t=1602840909\" width=396 height=56 /></span><br><br>You solve easy puzzles and overcome light platforming challenges as you go Always Down.<br>The deeper you dissapear into the cave, the more you change.<br>You can do things you could have never thought to be possible!<br><br>... but<br><br><strong>is it really worth it?</strong><br><br>Always down is a ~10 minute long meditation on change that will stay with you for a long time.<br><br>The Steam Capsule Image was created by the wonderful @_cobywin",
